I made several modifications on hand-cranked generator MKII, but the final result was still unacceptable.
I posted my test results on a facebook forum and, surprisingly, gained some attention and feedback.

One of them told me that I should modify the electric current instead of using two-way to one-way mechanism.
I can make use of the "bridge rectifier" unit to unify the direction of current with a price which is slight loss of voltage.

Moreover there are many suppliers on online-shopping sites can offer this kind of semiconductor components.
The prices are not expensive at all.
They costs only 10 to 40 NTD per unit.

I'll keep developing the next version of hand-cranked generator based on this concept.
And I'll keep posting my results on the facebook forum, see if I can get more responses and attention from the community.

Currently there are two main goals for MKIII.
The first is to simplify and fortify the structure of the system.
The second is to increase the gear ratio, since it was not enough during the previous tests.
This time i'm going to make a system which accelerate rotation speed by 256 times.
With higher voltage output, the loss of energy will be reduced.

That land administration agent who mad troubles for us was still ding ill things.
He tried to fools and other landlords into signing up agreements that will damage our right.
But there's as landlord who have some knowledge in law and seemed to know how to deal with these accusations.
He also know there was a property developer behind this land administration agent.
Its members even include some politicians.
Some land around here were already "legally" stolen by them.
The law is not the tool to stop crimes, it's the vicious weapon forged by those mobs of law.

